title: They See Me Trollblin
description: The tiny Kotassians hire the Warriors to exterminate two humongous Trollblins that have invaded their village, but it turns out that the Trollblins are actually nice guys and the Warriors switch sides to protect them in a Kotassiam/Trollblin War!

title: UG Christmas Special
description: Santa and Uncle Grandpa must work through their personal differences order to save Christmas.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Random Acts of Memory
description: The Warriors learn that Nohyas has been using a Selective Memory Magisword to erase select interactions with Prohyas' bizarre doppelganger their entire lives, so their new mission: take back that sword!

title: In Dreams
description: Steven's dreams start broadcasting onto his bedroom TV.

title: Second Christmas
description: The Titans trick Starfire into believing in second Christmas with second Santa.

title: Saving Faith
description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

title: Drilling Deep
description: At school, Aki struggles with the side effects of his newly replicated Drill Man schematics; later, as Mega Man, he learns to control his Fire Powers in thwarting Drill Man's assault on Skyraisers Inc.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Three Gems and a Baby
description: Greg tells Steven the story of his first winter with Steven.

title: El eslabon mas debil
description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Omni-Copped
description: When Grandpa Max's engineer buddy Phil Billings gifts Team Tennyson the Omni-Copter, a state of the art flying vehicle that can transport the Rustbucket for overseas adventures, Steam Smythe takes to the skies to ground Ben and company's first test flight; but unbeknownst to our heroes, Smythe was sent to battle Ben's latest alien forms by a mysterious, powerful enemy: the Forever Knight.

title: Elect to Decline
description: Noville wants to impress Vambre with a new Magisword from the Cave of Stuff, but the Cave Weirdos are in election mode and horrible smear campaigning is making Noville's simple task impossible!

title: The More You Moe, the Moe You Know
description: Moe visits the tree house with a special birthday surprise for BMO. While BMO's mission stands on the brink of disaster, Finn & Jake host a strange guest.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: The Scientist Part 2
description: While Hot Rod and Soundwave battle the indestructible Scientist, Perceptor and the rest of the team attempt a mass breakout from the Loop.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: My Fair Achi
description: V&V enter Achi in a dog show competition to win a golden trophy, but their overbearing ways drive Achi to the edge.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Together Forever
description: Connie has a really clear vision for her future. Steven wants to make sure he'll be a part of it.

title: Mr. Universe
description: Greg takes Steven on the road to find the origins of the Universe name.

title: 'Twas the Fight Before Christmas
description: When Princess Morbucks tries to ruin Christmas for the children of the world, the Powerpuff Girls must save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: Videodrone
description: Mega Man must stop Hypno Woman from turning the students and teachers at Silicon Central into her mindless drones.

title: No Day Like Snow Day
description: When a blizzard hits the town, Master Frown tries to ruin everyone's fun by pretending to be a magical snowman! But when he gets frozen inside, Master Frown must worry less about ruining everyone's good time and instead not turning into a Frown-sicle, while he's forced to experience the joys of the holiday season!

title: The Christmas Special
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to destroy a gift for Santa to save Christmas.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Un dia nevado
description: Cuando una tormenta de nieve llega a la ciudad, Master Frown trata de arruinar la diversión de todos fingiendo ser un muñeco de nieve mágico. Pero cuando se congela por dentro, Master Frown debe preocuparse menos por arruinar la diversión de todos y más por no convertirse en un témpano malhumorado, imientras se ve obligado a experimentar la alegría de la temporada navideña!

title: Poles Apart
description: A trip to the South Pole goes upside down when Team Tennyson lands on the North Pole instead, but Ben quickly discovers the culprits: Solar & Polar Twain, magnetically-powered scientists who want to hold the world ransom by threatening to reverse Earth's magnetic poles!

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 2
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Merry Christmas Mordecai
description: Mordecai has to get through a Christmas party with C.J. without messing everything up.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: El Arbol Perfecto
description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

title: Return of Thermometron 9000
description: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

title: Christmas Parties
description: The Bears have been invited to all their friends' Christmas parties. In an effort to have time to crash Nom Nom's huge star-studded bash, the Bears first try to make quick stops at all their friends' parties throughout the night.

title: The Weakest Link
description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

title: Hideous Hound
description: Prohyas pets an unsightly stray dog, and from that moment on the poor pooch appears on a variety of Warrior missions, driving Vambre and Vambre's brain insane!

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Trouble Busters!/French Fry Wars
description: Trouble Busters!: Now that the Awesome Brawlers are world famous Bakugan experts, they want to help people solve their Bakugan-related problems. When the world's quietest town is experiencing unexplained noises, the Awseome Brawlers are called in to get to the bottom of it./French Fry Wars: The Awesome Brawlers are arguing over who gets to eat the last french-fry. At first, each member makes a case for why they should to be the one to eat it. But the quarrel quickly escalates into trash talk and revealing secrets about one another. With everyone now upset, things take an unexpected turn.

title: Ener-G-Shoes
description: When Vic uses trickery to buy a pair of super cool sneakers from Maria Teresa's yard sale, the shoes try to walk him to his demise as punishment.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Secret Santa
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the crew all have the same popular and hard-to-find gift in mine for their Secret Santa, their nice Christmas shopping trip to the mall turns into a crazy competition.

title: Christmas in Space
description: The guys celebrate their first Christmas in space by opening presents, eating peppermint bark and telling Christmas stories. Benson wants the stories to be more Christmas-y but the guys keep adding scary elements, which only infuriate their boss.

title: Growing Pains
description: Steven visits a doctor for the first time.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 1
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: La Cucarachita
description: When Vic's beloved pet cockroach dies, Vic turns to Charlene's dark magic to bring her back to life.

title: The Guest
description: Vic & Val blame each other for eating all the food in the kitchen and making a huge mess! However, they soon discover that a ghost is actually to blame! They enlist the help of Achi to unlock the world of spirits among them and kick the ghost out of their house!

title: Just Like Robots
description: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when the baddie uses their digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing our heroes to act unpredictably.

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Nice on Ice
description: An "unscheduled" TV appearance not only lands Aki in hot water for missing class, but sets Ice Man on a misguided mission to "unite" (i.e. freeze together) every human and robot couple in the city!

title: Omnicoptero
description: Cuando el ingeniero Phil Billings, amigo del Abuelo Max, le regala al equipo Tennyson el Omni-Copter, un vehículo volador de última generación que puede transportar el Rustbucket hasta aventuras en el extranjero, Vapor Smythe sube a los cielos para obligar a aterrizar el primer vuelo de prueba de Ben y su familia. Pero sin que nuestros héroes lo sepan, Smythe fue enviado a combatir las formas alienígenas más nuevas de Ben por un misterioso y poderoso enemigo: el Caballero por Siempre.

title: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call/Phantom Thief Ajit
description: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call: An archeological discovery is made in Los Volmos. Exploration at the site is cut short, when a master thief and his apprentice attempt to steal the ancient Bakugan artifacts. When the Awesome Brawlers hear the news, they step in to thwart the thieves./Phantom Thief Ajit: An Ancient Bakugon artifact from an archeological discovery is placed in the Los Volmos Museum. The Awesome Brawlers are charged with guarding the artifacts from any further attempts thievery.

title: Los Jovenes Titanes Salvan la Navidad
description: Santa renuncia a la Navidad, y los Titanes deben intervenir para salvar la festividad.

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: Please Rush Home
description: A misunderstanding between Mega Man and Rush ends in the robo-pup running away from home, only to be reunited and reconciled during a confrontation with Wave Man.

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: Halloween vs. Navidad
description: Cuando Santa Claus intenta apoderarse de Halloween, los Titanes necesitan a un par de espíritus para detenerlo.

title: Winter Forecast
description: Steven has to get Connie home before it snows.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: Lecciones para un maestro
description: Cuando el Barón de Hierro obliga a Wu a tomar la Armadura de Dragón, las cosas no salen como se planearon. En Ninjago, hay un límite de lo que Lloyd puede soportar mientras se aferra a la esperanza del regreso de los Ninjas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Blaze of Glory
description: Mega Man and Suna must overcome a sibling dispute over what to do on their day off in order to stop Fire Man from overheating the city.

title: Teen Titans Save Christmas
description: Santa calls it quits so the Titans must pitch in to save the holiday.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: This One Goes to 11
description: During one last stop by a toy store before Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max's maiden voyage across the Atlantic, Ben runs into an old bully, Kevin 11, who now has new powers. He's able to transform into aliens just like Ben, such as the bootleg doppelganger of Cannonbolt. Wreckingbolt!

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: Snow Tubing
description: Rigby wants Eileen to go snow tubing.

title: Baku-Gear/Bakugan Rock!
description: Baku-Gear: The Awesome Brawlers are excited over their discovery of Baku-Gear, and want to get some footage of it in action. While they're filming, an underclassman named Trey challenges Dan to battle. Who will emerge victorious in the impromptu battle?/Bakugan Rock!: Baku-gear has shown up twice for Dan and Drago and it's starting to eat away at the other awesome brawlers. It's time they take it into their own hands. When Lia and Wynton go up against the rockin' new brawlers in town, they show Dan and Drago that they are not the only one who can summon this cool new tool!

title: Lords of Ghost Town
description: When V&V recruit a ghost to scare away a bully, they end up messing with the realm of the dead, which has disastrous consequences.

title: The True Meaning of Christmas
description: Fed up with never getting presents from Santa, the Titans head to the north pole to take themselves off the Naughty List by any means necessary.

title: The Prisoner Part 2
description: The dysfunctional team capture a Sharkticon bailiff and Soundwave's attempts to sabotage Hot Rod's leadership don't go as planned.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Two Lies, One Truth
description: As Lloyd unmasks Mystake for who she truly is, Emperor Garmadon embraces Harumi as his daughter of darkness. Meanwhile, Wu holds onto faith as he leads his friends into dangerous Oni territory in the hope of finding Firstbourne's nest

title: The Two Blades
description: In order to escape the Skull Sorcerer's chain-gang, the ninja must convince the Munce and Geckles to put aside their distrust and work together… by promising them something they may not be able to deliver -- The Blades of Deliverance!

title: Vote Gumball…and Bobert?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. He turns his attention to Bobert, the school's electronic wonderkid - but does Gumball really fit into his equation? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Bismuth Casual
description: Pearl invites Bismuth to the roller rink for a lesson on how to forge human relationships.

title: The Prisoner Part 1
description: Hot Rod and Soundwave compete over leadership of the group, arguing over how to best defeat the Quintessons.

title: The Alliance Part 1
description: Freed from the Loop, Optimus and Megatron still have trouble reconciling so it's up to Hot Rod and Soundwave to unite the divided Cybertronians against the Quintesson invaders.

title: Salvando a Faith
description: Lloyd y su equipo planean tomar el control del Oni Titan. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, los Ninja caen en las garras del Barón de Hierro y un viejo maestro regresa.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Escuela De Payasos
description: Mientras Ben disfruta en el estacionamiento a la salida de un partido de fútbol americano de ex estudiantes de la Universidad de State, se alía con los antiguos compañeros del Abuelo Max para impedir que Zombozo, un payaso demente, le robe a todo el público durante el entretiempo.

title: El regreso de Thermometron 9000
description: Durante una ola de calor brutal, Axel y su equipo deben rastrear Thermometron 9000, robado por Ice Crusher para dos propósitos: ievitar que su pista de hockey se derrita y cebar los buenos juguetes en una revancha!

title: Green Destiny
description: The Ninja finally return home and unite to stop Emperor Garmadon, forcing Lloyd to make a decision that will forever change Ninjago.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: White Elephant Gift Exchange
description: The park guys want revenge on Muscle Man for all his terrible gifts.

title: You're a Good Man, Mojo Jojo
description: The holidays are Mojo's favorite time…for ruining everything! But this year, he may just learn the reason for the season.

title: Getting Ahead
description: When the headless body of Omnibus knocks at their door, the Warriors use Magiswords to try to make a head they can talk to with mixed results!

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Rebelion En La Granja
description: Ben encuentra el laboratorio secreto del Doctor Ánimo -ahora gobernado por los alfas, sus mutantes superiores- y debe ayudar a los animales inferiores mientras está atrapado en forma de Insectoide.

title: Lessons for a Master
description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Into the Dark
description: When Cole investigates a mysterious visitor, the ninja aren't sure what to believe. Cole is frustrated with this lack of team support, until Princess Vania reveals a secret entrance that leads to an underground mine beneath Shintaro - where the city's dark secrets are held.

title: Brawler Headhunting/Lightning's Entrance Exam
description: Brawler Headhunting: As acting president of Kazami International, Shun is called upon to entertain another new young CEO Luca Schmidt, who's interested in doing business with the Kazami International. But Shun quickly realizes something is up when Luca tries woo him over to his brawling team - the Glanz Five. /Lightning's Entrance Exam: The Awesome Brawlers may be world famous heroes, but that doesn't mean they get out of going to school. They are still regular kids, doing regular kid things. But teachers may have something to say when Lightening decides he wants to join his buddies in the classroom.

title: Game Over
description: Unagami breaks into the real world and terrorizes Ninjago City while Jay, Zane and Pixal attempt to prevent disaster by reuniting Unagami with his creator, Milton Dyer.

title: The Mysterious Boy/A New Power
description: The Mysterious Boy: After stopping Tiko's rampage, the Awesome Brawlers have become world-famous heroes and Bakugan-mania sweeps the globe. With the Bakugan boom, brawling has been reinvented as a sporting game. In celebration of the Awesome Brawlers efforts, a tournament is being held in their honor. But the battles are quickly cut short when a rogue brawler and his golden Bakugan crash the event./A New Power: A Rogue brawler, Agit and his golden Bakugan have crashed the Awesome Brawlers party. Who is this brawler? How can he control a Golden Bakugan? Only one way to find out - Bakugan Brawl! Dan and Drago go head to head with the outsides to get to the bottom of it. Outmatched by their opponent, Dan and Drago get a little help from a new powerful weapon - Baku-Gear.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Shintaro
description: The ninja are invited to attend the birthday party of Princess Vania, in the distant Kingdom of Shintaro. They depart, bringing along Master Wu, unaware that he is feeling his age…

title: Vote Gumball…and Leslie?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. He hopes Leslie's newfound cheer-team fame will elevate his campaign, but Leslie won't play ball. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Christmas
description: Santa Claus is coming to town. Unfortunately he gets run over by the Wattersons, so it's up to them to save Christmas.

title: Halloween vs. Christmas
description: When Santa tries to take over Halloween, it's up to the Titans and a few ghouls to stop him.

title: Christmas Crusaders
description: Santa Claus and Robin must stop the nefarious Coal Miner.

title: Vote Gumball…and Anyone?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. He is running out of options - will anybody, or anything, be his vice president? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Stop the Presses
description: Richard's newspapers aren't selling, so his friends pull out all the stops to put the printed word back on top.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Peliculas Navidenas
description: En Nochebuena, los Osos bebé impiden un robo en una tienda de videos.

title: Castles and Kitties
description: Score Creeper traps the gang in a fantasy role playing game where they must follow a complex set of rules to win their freedom.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Power Outage
description: A ghoul known as Calythos possesses the Parasite in order to drain the Justice League of its powers and use that stolen strength to open a massive volcano.

title: Party Animal
description: Green Arrow, who is determined to finally throw a successful holiday party for the Justice League, finds his plans thwarted when Plastic Man brings a tranquilized super villain to the gathering.

title: Prince Starling's Quest
description: Lion-O is happily playing with Snarf in their "Frolicking Field" and doesn't have a care in the world, unfortunately he's accidentally stomping all over the miniature village of the Micrits! The tiny people want to defeat the "giant orange monster" but such a quest would require a brave hero. Luckily, the Micrits have such a hero: Prince Starling! Now, let us the tell you the epic tale of Prince Starling as he journeys to find the fountain of growth and defeat the wicked Lion-O, who has no idea any of this is going on!

title: Como Robots
description: Axel y el equipo se ven superados por Madcap cuando el malo usa sus dispositivos digitales para rastrear cada uno de sus movimientos en combate, lo que obliga a nuestros héroes a actuar de manera impredecible.

title: The Scientist Part 1
description: In order to heal Soundwave's glitch and find out how to free the Autobots and Decepticons from the Loop, the team hunt down a mysterious Quintesson called The Scientist.

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: The Alliance Part 2
description: Autobots and Decepticons unite, launching a massive assault on the Quintesson ship.

title: Dos mentiras una verdad
description: Cuando Lloyd desenmascara y revela la identidad de Mystake, el Emperador Garmadon acepta a Harumi como su hija de la oscuridad. Mientras tanto, Wu se aferra a su fe al llevar a sus amigos hacia territorios Oni peligrosos esperando encontrar el nido de la Primogénita.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Ratar-O
description: The ThunderCats have gotten so good at defeating the Mutants of Plun-Darr that it's basically become routine. That all changes with the arrival of the Mutants' old leader: Ratar-O, wielder of the Sword of Plun-Darr! Uh-oh!

title: Thank You
description: The Snow Golem and his beseeching pup pay a visit to the Fire Kingdom.

title: The Worst Rescue Ever
description: The ninja attempt to rescue Cole, but the bickering of his fellow prisoners, the Geckles and Munce, alerts the Skull Sorcerer, and soon the ninja are prisoners too.

title: Destino verde
description: Los Ninjas regresan por fin a casa y se unen para detener al Emperador Garmadon, obligando a Lloyd a tomar una decisión que cambiará por siempre a Ninjago.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol
